item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Subnet_Registration_SubnetReference
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Subnet_Registration_SubnetReference Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Network_Subnet_Registration_SubnetReference is provided to reference [[SoftLayer_Network_Subnet_Registration]] object and the [[SoftLayer_Network_Subnet]] it references, in CIDR form. Local registrationId The ID of the [[SoftLayer_Network_Subnet_Registration]] object. Type: integer subnetCidr The subnet address in CIDR form. Type: string
